 in conspiratorial narratives to the present day although writers of the post era have tended to play down their importance   markku ruotsila  antisemitism in peter knight conspiracy theories in american history an encyclopedia abcclio p  this new economic antisemitism issued in a variety of fullblown conspiracy theories in the s through the s in these conspiracy theories all the perceived evils of modern capitalism and industrialism were ascribed to jews  and on a more precise level because of the purported machinations of identifiable jewish financiers the latter type of theories tended to center around the supposed power of the rothschild banking family and those of its us agents that were central in various reconstruction and public debt refinancing schemes after the civil war   richard allen landes and steven t katz  the paranoid apocalypse a hundredyear retrospective on the protocols of the elders of zion nyu press p   there are antisemitic claims of a vast conspiracy by jews that structurally replicate the protocols without mentioning the hoax document another way conspiracy theories try to avoid the label of antisemitic is to argue that there is a vast conspiracy by the rothschild family or the khazars or some other entity   david norman smith  antisemitism in carl skutsch encyclopedia of the worlds minorities  af routledge p  the great banking barons of the rothschild family became in antisemitic fantasy living emblems of jews everywhere  for antisemites socialism and bank capitalism are just two sides of the jewish conspiracy against order and tradition   michael streeter  behind closed doors the power and influence of secret societies new holland publishers p  when it comes to conspiracy theories and the secret societies that supposedly run out world  the finger of suspicion often points to bankers and jews  and often to jewish bankers  as the moneymen behind this world plot chief among the suspects are the rothschilds the jewish banking dynasty  yet there is little or nothing that the rothschild bankers have done that is not perfectly explicable by normal banking practices  he fact that the rothschilds feature at the centre of so many conspiracy theories is perhaps no coincidence for it is sadly the case that many claims alleging secret societies have contained more than a tinge of antisemitism   nicholas goodrickclarke  black sun aryan cults esoteric nazism and the politics of identity nyu press p  conspiracy theorist jan van helsings dubious sources his constant repetition of jewish names as members of private and public organizations and above all his emphasis on the assets and powerbroking influence of the rothschilds as the top illuminati family leave no doubt that his conspiracy theories are aimed at jewish targets   morton fredreric the rothschilds a family portrait secker  warburglondon uk  burkes peerage baronetage  knightageth ed  all in this together osborne is skiing zac goldsmith is in £kaweek villa and mr speaker hosting a lavish party for mps as britain faces year of austerity simon walters and lara gould daily mail london  january   a b c s charles mosley editor burkes peerage baronetage  knightage th edition  volumes wilmington delaware usa burkes peerage genealogical books ltd  volume  page  hereinafter cited as burkes peerage and baronetage th edition  francesco rapazzini élisabeth de gramont paris fayard   ecowarrior sets sail to save oceans from plastic death the observer london  april  robin mckie  annemyriam dutrieue le baron léon lambert un banquier et financier belge d’envergure internationale du xxe siècle   the rothschilds and their  years of political influence andy mcsmith  october  the independent london  grand fortunes dynasties of wealth in france algora publishing  by michel pinçon monique pinçoncharlot andrea lyn secara page   young love will cement marriage of britains top three dynasties ingrid mansell the times london  april   carola w rothschild exgirl scout official new york times  september   druon maurice ces messieurs de rothschild paris   charles mosley editor burkes peerage baronetage  knightage th edition  volumes wilmington delaware usa burkes peerage genealogical books ltd  volume  page  hereinafter cited as burkes peerage and baronetage th edition  baron etienne van zuylen van nijevelt van de haar and baroness hélène de rothschild  charles mosley editor burkes peerage baronetage  knightage th edition  volumes wilmington delaware usa burkes peerage genealogical books ltd  volume  page  hereinafter cited as burkes peerage and baronetage th edition  us magazine nicky hilton is engaged to james rothschild hotel heiress to marry banking heir by esther lee and brody brown  august   rebecca pocklington  july  mr  mrs first pictures of nicky hilton and james rothschild on their wedding day as she flashes her garter mirror   a b jewish heraldry heraldicaorg  further reading niall ferguson the house of rothschild moneys prophets – isbn  niall ferguson the house of rothschild the worlds banker – isbn  frederic morton the rothschilds portrait of a dynasty isbn x amos elon founder a portrait of the first rothschild and his time  isbn  egon caesar conte corti rise of the house of rothschild b lunn translator books for business  reprint of  translation published by gollancz isbn  amazoncouk searchable online view joseph valynseele  henriclaude mars le sang des rothschild lintermédiaire des chercheurs et curieux paris  isbn  derek a wilson rothschild a story of wealth and power isbn x mirbabayev mf the role of azerbaijan in the worlds oil industry – oilindustry history usa  v  no  p – mirbabayev mf the rothschild brother’s contribution to baku’s oil industry – oilindustry history usa  v  no  p – documentary film ascent of money a financial history of the world – the early history of the rothschilds family business feature in the second of a fourpart series by niall ferguson aired on channel four external links wikimedia commons has media relate